{"title":"娘的来信","authors":["丘丁"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":11,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"娘的来信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丘丁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个战士的母亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——小丘子的娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来信这样讲："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“儿啊！你穿上棉衣裳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别惦记家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也别想娘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大水淹了咱的房和地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱不单靠政府来救济。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你爹还不算老，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我还跑得动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靠着两只手，什么也不"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他纺线，我织布，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拾掇起老行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赚了吃，顾了穿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的战士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"娘的心肠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿啊！永远拿着枪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿忙娘也忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记住娘的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿儿早上功臣榜。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十一、三于军大"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}